{"tid":508540,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"新垣結衣（236）「Merry Christmas」","createTime":"2017-12-24T10:59:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-24T11:14:03.000Z","uid":25382,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"19cd76eb0b075d7097a501662d3c83f2672b995b","tid":508540,"uid":25382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T10:59:09.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rC72OXT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FrC72OXT.png&h=8b3c0232&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n-新post格式：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/1jRJUk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F1jRJUk&d=iaPIFLljQiWMhXbcj5qflcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=c1b663d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/1jRJUk</a><br />\n- <strong>2樓入門攻略、投票區、綜藝<br />\n廣告、相集、Google drive綜合下載</strong><br />\n- 3樓新劇/電影資訊<br />\n<br />\n-頭post出齊先好留名 記得正皮<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Ul7S4Mn.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FUl7S4Mn.gif&h=c75e1702&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/v8rgmyt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fv8rgmyt.png&h=49d0d8d3&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>標題來源：</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/xULW8jqq2jVyn1fLmU/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FxULW8jqq2jVyn1fLmU%2Fgiphy.gif&h=019336de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>2018掛曆/枱曆</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7jfYPvL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F7jfYPvL.jpg&h=e0b37c78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n周邊產品攻略：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/CtQfX9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FCtQfX9&d=iaPIFLljQiWMhXbcj5qflcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=218ed3e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/CtQfX9</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/BT0s9K7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FBT0s9K7.png&h=babee597&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>結衣畫畫活動</strong></span></span><br />\n自己揀一個場面黎畫（唔一定畫結衣）<br />\n畫風、畫畫工具不限 題材跟結衣出演既作品 每期轉一套<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今期係<strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">S 最後的警官</span></strong></span><br />\n每10個post就會一次過po作品<br />\n今期畫作會出係post <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">235</span></strong>  <br />\n已完成畫作可以Email比那年巴<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Email：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n附上作品時唔該俾埋Lihkg User Name同ID<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">另外建議大家影自己作品個時可以用App: Office Lens/CamScanner去影<br />\n會有Scan嘅效果,不過並非硬性規定一定要用</span></div>"},{"pid":"131327dc953906352371ec1a3157e3e1f6bb2c3a","tid":508540,"uid":25382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T10:59:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>新手上路主線攻略</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/TnYOcs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FTnYOcs&d=iaPIFLljQiWMhXbcj5qflcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=48d7163a\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/TnYOcs</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">日劇冷知識：</span></strong><br />\n日本無分男 / 女主角呢樣野<br />\n得一個主演，好少會有雙主演<br />\n例如結衣係主演，星野源就要係助演<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>周邊產品攻略</span><br />\n(官方月曆、CD、代言產品等等)</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/CtQfX9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FCtQfX9&d=iaPIFLljQiWMhXbcj5qflcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=218ed3e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/CtQfX9</a><br />\n<br />\n大量舊雜誌訪問(整理、收集：仙人巴)<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/bhc9Qr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fbhc9Qr&d=iaPIFLljQiWMhXbcj5qflcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=7d3377b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/bhc9Qr</a><br />\n<br />\nB站Gakki綜藝連結<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/0h1G6W\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F0h1G6W&d=iaPIFLljQiWMhXbcj5qflcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=f9e0e5c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/0h1G6W</a><br />\n<br />\nGakki全廣告(Google Drive)<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/9V58zL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F9V58zL&d=iaPIFLljQiWMhXbcj5qflcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=962011e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/9V58zL</a><br />\n<br />\n新垣結衣 高清CM 171連發<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bilibili.com/video/av8228403\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bilibili.com%2Fvideo%2Fav8228403&d=iaPIFLljQiWMhXbcj5qflcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=d002429c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bilibili.com/video/av8228403</a><br />\n<br />\n~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>綜合下載寶庫(由星空巴提供)</strong></span></span><br />\n隔離登pm Gmail比「星空下的緣份」巴打等批<br />\n無舊登ac擺係到睇運氣，請耐心等候<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>綜合下載寶庫2號(由米羅巴提供)</strong></span><br />\n擺Email去<a href=\"https://goo.gl/sdsosi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fsdsosi&d=iaPIFLljQiWMhXbcj5qflcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=43386185\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/sdsosi</a>，請耐心等候<br />\n[所有劇集、電影於星空寶庫]<br />\n常見問題：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/8G91mP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F8G91mP&d=iaPIFLljQiWMhXbcj5qflcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=ad5b8b3e\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/8G91mP</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Google Drive圖庫(整理：米羅、196)</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/qXk2TG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FqXk2TG&d=iaPIFLljQiWMhXbcj5qflcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=f0aec511\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/qXk2TG</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s23.postimg.org/g2p80f3xn/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs23.postimg.org%2Fg2p80f3xn%2Fimage.jpg&h=de5a979b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s2.postimg.org/ezlnk1wk9/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs2.postimg.org%2Fezlnk1wk9%2Fimage.jpg&h=9bd77732&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>巴絲打區：</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n重點連結：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/yvoJwK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FyvoJwK&d=iaPIFLljQiWMhXbcj5qflcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=b34a7eb5\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/yvoJwK</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/BQxA8i5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FBQxA8i5.gif&h=fd7485c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCredit：華田"},{"pid":"db5e5c4af53affd3e918260cca98e9fc66d19527","tid":508540,"uid":25382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T10:59:28.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">《Code Blue 3》電影版製作決定！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/O1bGuox.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FO1bGuox.gif&h=e9026d1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n官網：<a href=\"http://www.fujitv.co.jp/codeblue/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fujitv.co.jp%2Fcodeblue%2F&d=iaPIFLljQiWMhXbcj5qflcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=d2459910\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.fujitv.co.jp/codeblue/</a><br />\nTwitter：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/code_blue2017\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcode_blue2017&d=iaPIFLljQiWMhXbcj5qflcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=2d8cb283\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/code_blue2017</a><br />\n預告：待補<br />\n上映時間：2018年7月27日(日本)<br />\n<br />\n出演：<br />\n山下智久、新垣結衣、戶田惠梨香、比嘉愛未<br />\n淺利陽介、有岡大貴、成田凌、新木優子<br />\n馬場富美加、安藤政信、椎名桔平<br />\nSTAFF：<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/khHqBVo.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FkhHqBVo.png&d=iaPIFLljQiWMhXbcj5qflcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=5ad87337\" target=\"_blank\">http://i.imgur.com/khHqBVo.png</a><br />\n<br />\n主題曲 - Mr.Children - HANABI<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VZ1q8VlF8Ao\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVZ1q8VlF8Ao&d=iaPIFLljQiWMhXbcj5qflcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=63cba240\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VZ1q8VlF8Ao</a><br />\n<br />\n　　時間設定於第2季的七年後，藍澤耕作（山下智久飾）離開了翔陽大學附屬北部醫院的急救中心，成為了一名神經外科醫生。白石惠<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">（新垣結衣飾）</span></strong>依然在人手不足的急救中心擔當著領導者的角色。曾經也夢想成為飛行急救醫生的緋山美帆子（戶田惠梨香飾）離開翔陽醫院，成為了婦產科醫生。冴島遙（比嘉愛未飾）依然從事著飛行急救護士的工作。藤川一男 （淺利陽介飾）與白石一起留在急救中心，成為了一名整形的急救醫生。<br />\n<br />\n關係圖：<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DBrncZZUQAAKdmC.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDBrncZZUQAAKdmC.jpg&d=iaPIFLljQiWMhXbcj5qflcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=4c81c1b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DBrncZZUQAAKdmC.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\ncb3官網新垣結衣採訪部分：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/6ovdUm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F6ovdUm&d=iaPIFLljQiWMhXbcj5qflcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=3b3f4ce2\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/6ovdUm</a>"},{"pid":"e192e28eeec6935ade07ccf905f104f7b091ebec","tid":508540,"uid":25382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T10:59:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SXK6GyE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FSXK6GyE.jpg&h=52d1d2ad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc705c44499f64075984eb4bd3bf82215bed6e8b","tid":508540,"uid":104613,"l